description.en:
KDOE is an ERC-20 utility token on the Ethereum blockchain and is an essential part of the Kudoe ecosystem. KDOE
is a versatile utility token that is used as the base currency for transactions within gaming and decentralized
applications , and the underlying currency for our governance protocol (DAO).
